headline: Does Williams-Sonoma (WSM) Still Offer Value After Its Strong Multi‑Year Share Price Run?
summary: If you have been wondering whether Williams-Sonoma's share price still reflects fair value after its recent run, you are not alone. The stock last closed at US$197.81, with returns of 10.8% over 7 days, 9.6% over 30 days, 5.3% year to date, 3.2% over 1 year, 225.9% over 3 years and 247.8% over 5 years, which naturally raises questions about what is already priced in.
